Author: Lars Kiesow <lkiesow@uos.de>
Date:   Tue Dec 13 16:07:50 2022 +0100

    Allow creating releases manually
    
    This patch is a quick workaround for the problem that the automatically
    cut release tags do not trigger the GitHub Actions workflow to create a
    release on GitHub. This patch allows committers to trigger the workflow
    manually.
